These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, fuchsia, black, red
City: rome, hannover, marseilles, new-york
1. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
2. the person who likes fuchsia is not the person traveling to rome##6
3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person who likes black is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
6. the person traveling to rome is not the person who likes black##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | fuchsia   | red    | blood-red    | black |
| Sport      | new-york | rome | marseilles | hannover |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bongani, old-henry, cain
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, august, october, june
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
2. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
3. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the cain-smoker##5
4. the bongani-smoker is not the person who's birthday is in august##6
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the cain-smoker is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
8. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the prince-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | bongani  | old-henry    | prince | cain    |
| Food       | june | august | october  | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
House: futuristic, tower, farmhouse, modern
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, turquise, white, green
1. the modern house is not the person who likes grey##6
2. the person who likes turquise is not the farmhouse house##6
3. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the tower house##3
4. the person who likes turquise is the futuristic house##1
5. the tower house is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
6. the futuristic house is in an odd position##4
7. the person who likes grey is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | modern       | tower  | futuristic  | farmhouse |
| Job        | white | green | turquise | grey  |

