.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, september, august, may
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, tennis, climbing, cricket
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
3. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
4. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | september | august | may     | january |
| Transport   | tennis     | climbing    | golf | cricket    |

