3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is not the person traveling to colone##6
5. the person traveling to prague is not the person who's hobby is camping##6
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | camping        | filmmaking | singing | traveling |
| Transport   | colone | prague | rome     | nizza   |

