.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, librarian, coach, engineer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, handball, skateboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the scientist##1
2. the engineer is not the person who's sport is handball##6
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the coach is the coach##1
6. the coach is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is sailing##5
7. the coach is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
8. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5
9. the librarian is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is soccer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | librarian | coach    | scientist  | engineer   |
| Nationality   | skateboarding  | soccer | handball | sailing |

