.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, lizard, chinchilla, cat
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, tea, iced-tea
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
2. the person drinking tea is not the owner of the lizard##6
3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
5. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the lizard is the person drinking 7up##1
7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | cat | lizard     | chinchilla | hedgehog |
| Music-Genre   | tea | 7up | iced-tea      | coffee         |

