There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, milk, cola
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the bolivar-smoker##5
3. the person drinking milk is not the dunhill-smoker##6
4. the aristoff-smoker is between the person drinking cola and the dunhill-smoker##2
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
6. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking juice and the bolivar-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | dunhill | aristoff    | bolivar | blend |
| Music-Genre   | juice         | sprite | cola   | milk     |

