4. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
5. the person eating avocado is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person eating eggplant##2
6. the person traveling to hamburg is not the person eating pumpkin##6
7. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | boston  | san-francisco | london | hamburg |
| Sport   | pumpkin | eggplant | avocado   | nectarine |

