1. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the dutch##5
2. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the chinese##5
3. the chinese is on the left of the colombian##1
4. the polish is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
5. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in january##2
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
8. the polish is somewhere to the right of the chinese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | january | december | february | september |
| Pet     | dutch  | chinese      | colombian  | polish       |

