.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, indonesian, chinese, german
4 different games are played: poker, backgammon, billiard, scrabble
1. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
2. the german is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing poker is not the brazilian##6
5. the german is somewhere to the right of the person playing backgammon##5
6. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | brazilian | indonesian | german      | chinese   |
| Transport   | scrabble  | backgammon   | billiard | poker |

 